// 256 MiB. tmpfs/page-cache data lives in the kernel heap, and LTP mmap3 keeps
// up to ~40 concurrent multi-MiB tmpfs files alive at once (peak ~160 MiB of
// file data) — the previous 192 MiB (0xC00_0000) heap was exhausted at peak
// (panic in heap_allocator; see docs/mmap3-heap-oom.md).
